column4: Daimler plans at least six electric car models: source
column5: FRANKFURT German carmaker Daimler  plans to roll out at least six  and possibly as many as nine  electric car models as part of its push to compete with Tesla  and Volkswagen's  Audi  a person familiar with Daimler's plans told Reuters.
